    <center><h1>Bangladesh</h1></center>

    <h2>About Bangladesh</h2>
    <p>Bangladesh is a country located in South Asia, sharing borders with India and Myanmar.</p>

    <h3>Geography</h3>
    <p>Bangladesh is characterized by fertile plains, the Ganges-Brahmaputra delta, and numerous rivers.</p>

    <h3>Capital</h3>
    <p>The capital of Bangladesh is Dhaka, a vibrant and bustling city.</p>

